tags.name: Civitan Park
tags.note: Laramie County School District 1 has absorbed Civitan Park by demolishing the existing older Goings Elementary shown on OSM, while building a new school onto the north end of the lot shown as Civitan Park. Google map shows rebuilt school, on park site.

tags.name: Indian Village exhibition
tags.note: Cheyenne Frontier Park area Indian Village, recreating the dress, crafts, skills and designs of Indian culture in high plains of Wyoming. During late July the Cheyenne Frontier Days rodeo festival.

tags.name: Brimmer Park
tags.note: Community Park, Cheyenne, Wy, skate park, playground, softball fields, picnic area, next to East High School and Veterans Hospital.

tags.name: Cheyenne Frontier Park
tags.note: This area famous for the largest U.S. outdoor rodeo, in July, and also the Old West Museum open all year. Seating for 19,000 in the arena, plus Frontier Town, Indian Village, Carnival Midway and Saloon during rodeo.

tags.name: Cheyenne Depot Plaza
tags.note: Public festivals, music, barbecues, pancake breakfasts, farmers markets, with shelters, restrooms, parking when not in use as event center, brewery restaurant, museum.

tags.name: David R. Romero South Cheyenne Community Park
tags.note: David Romero Community Park, Center and Youth Activity center. Newest 2012 park. Softball field, playground with soft base, climbing wall, shelters and plenty of room to play. Reserve indoor play areas. Indoor climbing wall too.

tags.name: Holliday Park
tags.note: Lake improvements underway. Art Center, playground, restrooms, 4 tennis courts, volleyball, picnic shelters, new greenway tunnel passes under East Lincolnway to southeast trail.

tags.name: Martin Luther King Jr. Park
tags.note: playground, basketball, baseball, restrooms, picnic, tennis, creek and greenway trail, walk to motels, restaurants, homeless shelter

tags.name: Cahill Park
tags.note: playground, bike trails, picnic shelters, rest rooms, soccer fields, new 100 car parking lot accessed by new street, restrooms, sculpture, on greenway

tags.name: Gunslinger Town
tags.note: Outdoor reenactment of western gunfights during summer months in Cheyenne

tags.name: Mylar Park
tags.note: playground, greenway, creek, pond, restroom, horseshoes, grills, disc golf, many parking areas

tags.name: Absarraca Park
tags.note: Large lake passing under Interstate 25, boat, fish, picnic, RV dump station at Kennedy Road, walk south to Lions Park and Frontier Days Rodeo Park
